videos.headline: Virginia 7-footer slams it down
videos.description: Marco Anthony drives and dishes to Virginia sophomore Jay Huff for a powerful one-handed dunk vs. Morgan State.

videos.headline: Virginia team manager assists for huge slam
videos.description: Virginia team manager Grant Kersey runs the fast break and feeds Austin Katstra for a two-handed jam late in the second half vs. Morgan State.

videos.headline: Virginia team manager Kersey makes and-1 layup
videos.description: Following an assisted dunk, Virginia team manager Grant Kersey cuts down the lane and Austin Katstra feeds him for a layup and a foul.

article.description: — Malik Miller scored 26 points and Morgan State defeated Virginia University of Lynchburg on Tuesday night.

article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Malik Miller scored 26 points and Morgan State defeated Virginia University of Lynchburg on Tuesday night. Khalil Turner added 21 points and Isaiah Burke 20 for the Bears (3-5). Marcus Willis led the Dragons with 25 points. ------
